briefdescription.para: Cereal does not support the serialization of raw pointer.

detaileddescription.para: This macro enable developers to serialize boost::variant that holds raw pointers by using the above PointerVariantWrapper class which replace the internal raw pointers by smart pointer internally.

parameterdescription.para: boost::variant that holds raw pointer to be serialized.

detaileddescription.para: Omar Shrit Implementation of a boost::variant wrapper to enable the serialization of the pointers inside boost variant in cereal
